        "TileImage": "$($repository 7d79859c-7b10-4978-8387-199526dc6220).Image",
        "Description": "Thanks for taking the job, dangerous bald man. Anyway this dude called me a &quot;permaclucked soma-smoking clown&quot; after he ran over my dog and I threatened legal action. Turns out he&apos;s in a local prepper cult and will probably shoot me if I press this further. They have a whole crazy compound and everything. I want you to sneak in there and choke him out. This CANNOT come back to me though, so keep it quiet and simple. We&apos;ll see who&apos;s the real clown. (Ideally wear a clown costume for extra irony.)",
